lead_paragraph: Wales named prop Rob Evans, winger Tom James and flanker Justin Tipuric in their starting team for the Six Nations opener against defending champions Ireland in Dublin on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Wales Name Evans, James to Face Ireland
